objects.name: Tutorial3
objects.string: Collect these items to gain points

objects.name: Tutorial4
objects.string:
Hearts refill your lives

Each life is worth 35 points

objects.name: Tutorial5
objects.string:
Throughout the game, you will meet various enemies
and you can kill them by jumping on them

Each enemy killed is worth 15 points

objects.name: Tutorial6
objects.string:
You can activate flags which
serve as checkpoints

When you die, you will respawn
at the last activated flag

objects.name: Tutorial7
objects.string: Be careful not to fall down

objects.name: Tutorial8
objects.string:
There are various traps which can be
deadly, so try your best to avoid them

objects.name: Tutorial9
objects.string:
You finish the level by
activating the yellow flag
